model
Class Shape

java.lang.Object
  model.Shape
Direct Known Subclasses:
Line, Oval, Picture, Rectangle
public abstract class Shape
extends java.lang.Object

This abstract class is the parent class to all shapes drawn in the Netpaint program. Provides the base methods needed to instantiate the various shape objects.

Author:
TannerKoch, JamesDeveuve

Constructor Summary
